OL,3,CProbe designed to study how clouds
OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FIt is the brainchild of Professor
OL,8,FAnthony Illingworth, from the
OL,9,FUniversity of Reading, who conceived
OL,10,Fthe idea more than 30 years ago.
OL,12,FThe project was adopted by the
OL,13,FEuropean Space Agency (ESA) in 2004,
OL,14,Fand later became a joint mission with
OL,15,Fthe Japanese space agency, Jaxa.
OL,17,FThorsten Fehr, ESA's EarthCARE mission
OL,18,Fscientist, described the launch as
OL,19,F"one of the greatest moments in my
OL,20,Fprofessional life".
