OL,7,FHe said: "It was just such an exciting
OL,8,Fmoment to see this perfect launch and
OL,9,Fdeployment of the satellite."
OL,11,FBjorn Frommknecht, ESA's EarthCARE
OL,12,Fmission manager, said: "I'm
OL,13,Fspeechless... it's very beautiful
OL,14,Femotions and very intense.
OL,16,F"We have been waiting for that
OL,17,F(EarthCARE satellite launch) for a
OL,18,Fvery long time."
