OL,3,CProbe designed to study how clouds
OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FClouds play a vital role in
OL,8,Fcontrolling the temperature of the
OL,9,Fplanet by reflecting sunlight back out
OL,10,Fto space and trapping heat.
OL,12,FBut little is known about how these
OL,13,Fdrive the Earth's climate system.
OL,15,FThe three-year mission, which cost
OL,16,Fmore than 800 million euros (#680
OL,17,Fmillion), is expected to provide
OL,18,Fanswers.
