OL,3,CProbe designed to study how clouds
OL,4,Caffect Earth's climate launched into
OL,5,Cspace
OL,7,FThe UK Space Agency (UKSA) contributed
OL,8,Faround 120 million euros (#102
OL,9,Fmillion) towards the mission over a
OL,10,Fperiod of 20 years.
OL,12,FThe satellite weighs just over two
OL,13,Ftonnes (2,200kg) and measures a little
OL,14,Fover 17 metres (56ft) in length.
OL,16,FOn board are four instruments that
OL,17,Fwill analyse cloud structures in
OL,18,Fdetail, take images, and measure how
OL,19,Fmuch heat from the Sun is being
OL,20,Ftrapped by clouds.
