OL,7,FRalph Cordey, head of Earth Science at
OL,8,FAirbus Space UK, said: "Today,
OL,9,FEarthCARE, the most complex satellite
OL,10,Fyet in ESA's Earth Explorer programme,
OL,11,Fstarts its three-year mission to
OL,12,Fimprove understanding of how heat
OL,13,Fflows in our planet's atmosphere.
OL,15,F"Airbus is delighted to have led the
OL,16,Fdevelopment of EarthCARE with the
OL,17,Fsupport of industries and agencies
OL,18,Facross Europe, Japan and North
OL,19,FAmerica."
